{
  "text": "Is there a best material or optimal size for the small pyramid to go beneath the head? I am Ra. Given that the proportions are such as to develop the spirals in the Giza pyramid, the most appropriate size for use beneath the head is an overall height small enough to make placing it under the cushion of the head a comfortable thing.",
